{"tid":729332,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱玩朗豪坊1on1場撚到個mk一棟都無","createTime":"2018-07-04T12:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T10:02:56.000Z","uid":15886,"like":81,"dislike":1115,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"781cd80a6281e656031a3d129f053d7ae9eaa48a","tid":729332,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:42:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱同朋友係朗豪坊行下 見到有個1on1場咪諗住入去玩下 反正有d腳痕  排緊隊個陣 聽到後面個mk同佢條女講到自己有幾勁 內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMk=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMk條女=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMk條女: bb你踢波係咪好勁？<br />\nMk: 緊係勁啦 我有個花名叫旺角尼馬 一陣睇我大炒d傻仔啦<br />\nMk條女: bb好叻叻呀<br />\n<br />\n我係前面忍唔住笑咗聲 好彩個mk聽唔到 <br />\n好啦 入場喇  我比佢攻先  <br />\n佢係到學尼馬咁fing下隻腳  <br />\n我完全無理佢  直接一腳ban埋去 <br />\n個mk即刻跌低咗 係咁碌黎碌去 <br />\n我忍唔住嘻咗一聲 條mk即刻企起身 話係咪認真？<br />\n但我無理佢 一拎到波就係咁ban埋去  入咗佢好多粒 之後完咗 個mk條女走埋我度 <br />\n同我講 你好射得 我都想試下比你射爆我 <br />\n跟住我就帶咗佢返屋企玩高速來回球<br />\n而家個套唔小心比我射穿咗  好驚條女會有咗 想問下咁多位巴打點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde1e3f0bf2d91cbad2ffab013da9a37eb908153","tid":729332,"uid":72475,"like":29,"dislike":262,"score":-233,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"4.5/10"},{"pid":"3487ce0c4662c2e5edd05af80b4a36a4f0a4913a","tid":729332,"uid":45772,"like":11,"dislike":10,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"6e546bd9111a6562ee587a6224839b4146c43b67","tid":729332,"uid":14222,"like":597,"dislike":8,"score":589,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:44:02.000Z","msg":"幽默感呢啲野..."},{"pid":"b8bbdc248913fc314598578f75c986d97dcfc55b","tid":729332,"uid":3161,"like":163,"dislike":11,"score":152,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:44:19.000Z","msg":"無是咁的<br />\n0分 重作"},{"pid":"977537478fdc857ca7765e8d4b822620ed389512","tid":729332,"uid":4525,"like":198,"dislike":3,"score":195,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-